@startuml
title SCORE — System Context

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

' --- ACTORS ---
actor "User" as User

' --- EXTERNAL SYSTEMS / SERVICES ---
cloud "Internet" as Internet {
  component "Weather API\n(Optional)" as WeatherAPI
  component "IP Geolocation\n(Optional)" as GeoIP
}

' --- SCORE SYSTEM BOUNDARY ---
rectangle "SCORE System" as SCORE {

  ' UI Layer
  package "UI Layer" {
    component "React SPA (Vite)" as REACT
    component "Mobile App (Android)\n(Future)" as ANDROID
  }

  ' API Layer
  package "API Layer" {
    component "Express API" as ExpressAPI
    component "FastAPI ML Service" as FastAPI
  }

  ' Perception (Optional)
  package "Perception Layer\n(Optional)" {
    component "Vision Inference\n(Model Weights)" as Vision
    component "Color Extraction\n(K-Means)" as Color
  }

  ' Persistence
  package "Database" {
    database "MongoDB" as MongoDB
  }

  ' Adapters / Ports
  package "Adapters (Ports)" {
    component "Weather Adapter" as WeatherAdapter
    component "Geo Adapter" as GeoAdapter
    component "Mongo Adapter" as MongoAdapter
    component "ML Client Adapter" as MLClient
  }
}

' --- USER INTERACTIONS ---
User --> REACT : forms + uploads
User --> ANDROID : camera + inputs\n(future)

' --- UI to Core ---
REACT --> ExpressAPI : HTTP requests
ANDROID --> ExpressAPI : HTTP requests\n(future)

' --- Core to internal components ---
ExpressAPI --> FastAPI : inference/scoring requests
ExpressAPI --> MongoAdapter : update preferences/feedback

' --- Core to storage via adapters ---
ExpressAPI --> MongoAdapter : load wardrobe/save feedback
MongoAdapter --> MongoDB

' --- Core to perception via adapters (optional) ---
ExpressAPI --> MLClient : analyze outfit photo (optional)
MLClient --> FastAPI

' --- External data via adapters (optional) ---
ExpressAPI --> WeatherAdapter : get weather label\n(optional)
ExpressAPI --> GeoAdapter : get coarse location\n(optional)

WeatherAdapter --> WeatherAPI
GeoAdapter --> GeoIP
WeatherAPI --> Internet
GeoIP --> Internet


note bottom of WeatherAdapter
Weather is an adapter: enriches context,
never required for core scoring.
end note

@enduml
